00:39:27.760 --> 00:39:33.410
work because we do God's work. We do good
stuff. Why do we, that's a genuine fault with

00:39:33.410 --> 00:39:40.349
us. You don't think about that and it's a
systematic, it's a systematic fault with how

00:39:40.349 --> 00:39:41.839
we think about conservation.

00:39:41.839 --> 00:39:46.339
So in the Solomons' case we do have some,
but the--the real sample we had were communities

00:39:46.339 --> 00:39:48.880
that had it and communities that didn't.

